# SydTek University
## Bachelor of Science in AI Systems

This repository contains the academic, governance, assessment, and accreditation-ready structure for the SydTek University undergraduate program in AI Systems.

## Mission
To prepare students to design, evaluate, govern, and deploy artificial intelligence systems across industry, education, research, entrepreneurship, and public-impact environments.

## Program Highlights
- AI integrated across the full curriculum
- Accreditation-aligned academic structure
- Outcomes-based learning model
- Ethics, governance, and responsible AI emphasis
- GitHub-native documentation model
- Workforce, research, and venture readiness

## Degree Requirements
- Core curriculum
- Major coursework
- Electives
- Capstone or applied project
- Total credits determined by official program map

## Institutional Affiliation Statement
This repository is affiliated with SydTek University and supports its academic, curriculum, and research infrastructure. It is structured in alignment with accreditation-oriented standards for future institutional review and continuous improvement.

